OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Ffading by the evening with cloudy
OL,7,Fperiods to follow. Cloud thickening by
OL,8,Fthe second half of the night with rain
OL,9,Fmoving in from the west later, turning
OL,10,Fpersistent and locally heavy over the
OL,11,FPennines.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA grey and wet start for some.
OL,14,FRain becoming widespread across the
OL,15,Farea with heavy outbreaks possible
OL,16,Fduring the afternoon and evening over
OL,17,Fwestern hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
