OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FUnsettled with spells of wet and windy
OL,7,Fweather with bands of rain moving
OL,8,Fthrough followed by brighter but
OL,9,Fshowery interludes. Temperatures
OL,10,Fdropping down to normal for the time
OL,11,Fof year.
